│ ## Initial Observations ##                                   │
│                                                              │
│ The reproducer is already minimized. Based on my experience  │
│ in debugging these bugs, the issue is likely introduced by   │
│ the *first transformation*, or due to incorrect analysis     │
│ information feeding into it.                                 │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first            │
│ transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass       │
│ regardless of whether it's in the                            │
│ `autofix/build/llvm-build/110295/bin/opt -p loop-vectorize   │
│ -S /tmp/reprod_y3lpo_4c.l` module or other modules.          │
│ #### Opt Information ####                                    │
│                                                              │
│ To gather more insight, I ran `opt` to inspect both the      │
│ transformations and the analysis results. Below are the      │
│ command and the resulting log:                               │
│                                                              │
│ ```bash                                                      │
│ $ bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -S --debug-only=                 │
│ /tmp/reprod_y3lpo_4c.ll                                      │
│ opt: llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp:7378:   │
│ llvm::VectorizationFactor                                    │
│ llvm::LoopVectorizationPlanner::computeBestVF(): Assertion   │
│ `(BestFactor.Width == LegacyVF.Width ||                      │
│ planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(BestFactor. │
│ Width), CostCtx, OrigLoop)) && " VPlan cost model and legacy │
│ cost model disagreed"' failed.                               │
│                                                              │
│ ```                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ From this log, I identified the first transformation point   │
│ as:                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ ```                                                          │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp::llvm::LoopV │
│ ectorizationPlanner::computeBestVF()                         │
